  <content>
    <chapter line="1">Paṭṭhānappakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</chapter>
    <gatha1 line="2">Devātidevo <pageBreak edition="Myanmar" number="0.0341" /><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0340" /> devānaṃ, devadānavapūjito,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="3">Desayitvā pakaraṇaṃ, yamakaṃ suddhasaṃyamo.</gathalast>
    <gatha1 line="4">Atthato dhammato ceva, gambhīrassātha tassa yaṃ,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="5">Anantaraṃ mahāvīro, sattamaṃ isisattamo.</gathalast>
    <gatha1 line="6">Paṭṭhānaṃ nāma nāmena, nāmarūpanirodhano,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="7">Desesi atigambhīra-nayamaṇḍitadesanaṃ.</gathalast>
    <gatha1 line="8">Idāni <pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0341" /> tassa sampatto, yasmā saṃvaṇṇanākkamo,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="9">Tasmā naṃ vaṇṇayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</gathalast>
